name: Message Command
description: Sends back the same message prefixed with 'Hello'. Useful for testing bot responses.

name: Purge Command
description: Deletes a specified number of recent messages. If a username is provided, only that user's messages are deleted.

name: Scan Channels Command
description: Scans all channels in the server and stores the retrieved data in the database for further analysis.

name: Scan Members Command
description: Scans all members in the server and stores the retrieved data in the database for further analysis.

name: Calculate Command
description: Evaluates a mathematical expression and returns the result.

name: Date Difference Command
description: Calculates the difference between two dates in days, weeks, and months.

name: Add Days Command
description: Adds or subtracts a specified number of days to or from a given date.

name: Day of the Week Command
description: Finds the day of the week for a specific date.

name: Age Command
description: Calculates the age in years, months, and days based on a given birthdate.

name: Generate Calendar Command
description: Generates a calendar for the specified month and year.

name: kick
description: Kicks a user from the server.

name: ban
description: Bans a user from the server.

name: mute
description: Mutes a user in the server.

name: unmute
description: Unmutes a user in the server.

name: warn
description: Warns a user in the server.

name: warnings
description: Fetches the warnings for a user.

name: lockdown
description: Locks down a text channel to prevent messages.

name: unlock
description: Unlocks a text channel to allow messages.

name: slowmode
description: Sets a slowmode delay in a channel.

name: addrole
description: Assigns a role to a user.

name: removerole
description: Removes a role from a user.

name: userinfo
description: Displays information about a user.

name: serverinfo
description: Displays information about the server.

name: temprole
description: Assigns a temporary role to a user for a specified duration.

name: softban
description: Bans and immediately unbans a user (softban).

name: poll
description: Creates a poll with a Yes/No reaction.

name: announce
description: Makes an announcement in a specified channel.

name: connect
description: Connects the bot to the user's voice channel.

name: disconnect
description: Disconnects the bot from the voice channel.

name: play
description: Plays a song from YouTube based on the search or URL.

name: pause
description: Pauses the current playback.

name: resume
description: Resumes the paused playback.

name: stop
description: Stops the current playback.

name: queue
description: Displays the current song queue.

name: skip
description: Skips the current song and plays the next one in the queue.
